                           <ab type="conservation">Only the upper margin is preserved in this light brown papyrus. It is broken off at the middle and lost the lower part to the right side as a result to perpendicular fold; the papyrus was also folded horizontally at the middle. Fibers at the left side are frayed and misaligned.</ab>
